'''''In the Name of Kephale''''' is an [[Adventure Mission]] on [[Amphoreus]] in the chapter [[Amphoreus Annals]].

==Steps==
# Speak with the guard to ask for entry
# Greet Serena before entering Dawncloud
# Take Serena around to explore Dawncloud
# Observe the giant mural
# Observe the other giant mural
# Continue deeper into Dawncloud toward Kephale's divine vessel
# Visit the Demigod Council
# Comfort Serena
# Proceed further into Dawncloud towards Kephale's divine vessel
# Approach Kephale and try speaking with the Titan
# Investigate the source of "Kephale's" voice
# Speak with Serena and escort her out of Dawncloud

